{"tid":2192583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"團結香港基金報告稱通識科教材無監管　須公布審核準則","createTime":"2020-09-07T08:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T08:49:31.000Z","uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18036c11cf6ac3d908ae7ffb9a95dead49f7aba9","tid":2192583,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"研究訪問25位教育專家、71位中學校長及484位通識科教師，就考評、課程、教材等多方面作出建議 。<br />\n<br />\n考評制度方面，基金會建議維持必修必考，但評分等級應由目前分七級，簡化為只評及格和不及格，大學收生只要及格就可以。基金會不同意這樣是矮化通識科。<br />\n<br />\n團結香港基金公共政策研究院院長黃元山：「如分成七級似乎精準性存疑，所以與其繼續考試為本，將其簡化為兩級或三級，能釋放更多師生的精力，真正享受通識帶來的目標。」<br />\n<br />\n通識課程現時168個課時，須教授六大單元，報告認為內容過於廣泛，建議刪減，但沒有明確建議刪減部分，只列出受訪教師希望刪減主題，依次為「自我了解」、「法治和社會政治參與」、「人際關係」等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=404655\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404655&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=fa3e3d33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404655&h=c0693d9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=404655</a><br />\n<br />\n教咗十年先話有問題，同母語教學一樣，改邊樣衰邊樣<br />\n唔怪得楊潤雄咁懶，要送仔去國際學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0745b9aeebcca66e3a4d70e03a8f3900c74385","tid":2192583,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"直接成科砍9左佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43db2358cf35e9ce0fd516ae3a96dee051ff9ecb","tid":2192583,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"當年邊個話開通識架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089da8603ee2e268ec9db04b728e116b737dbefa","tid":2192583,"ui